  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel &amp; Spa Le Savoie has an extremely convenient location on <a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere">Val d’Isère’s</a> central main street and a short walk to the ski lifts. The spa hotel is managed by Inghams, providing an informal and relaxed atmosphere for our British guests.</p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>Located on the main street of Val d'Isere the Hotel &amp; Spa Le Savoie has a prime position in resort. The Solaise Express lift for the Solaise and Le Fornet side of the ski area, or the Olympique gondola if you want to ski across towards <a data-udi="umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565" href="/{localLink:umb://document/204ce8e4cf8c4ab09205501e16cb7565}" title="Tignes">Tignes</a>, are just a short walk away from the hotel. </p>
<p>Sweeping stairs lead you from street level to the welcoming reception and fireside lounge area on the first floor. From here it opens into the attractive open-plan restaurant and bar. The smart interiors combine the warmth and traditional feel of wood, local stone and fine fabrics with stylish modern touches, creating a comfortable atmosphere.</p>
<p style="background-color: #003457; color: white; text-align: center;"><strong>Save up to 50% on child places when booking for the 2024/25 ski season!<br /></strong>Visit the Facilities tab below to find out more.</p>
<h2>Unwind and relax</h2>
<p>At the end of a day of exploring the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes-Val d'Isere Ski Area</a>, there is nowhere better to relax and unwind than the wellness area with an indoor pool. The extensive spa area is located on the ground floor of the hotel. Sooth your muscles and relax in the sauna or steam room, or enjoy lazing on the loungers with mountain views. </p>
<h2>Home cooked comforts</h2>
<p>The Hotel &amp; Spa Le Savoie is on a <span>half board basis which includes breakfast, afternoon tea and evening meals with wine included. There's a staff day off midweek when only breakfast is provided leaving you free to choose a restaurant of your choice. A </span>hearty breakfast buffet including a cooked breakfast, will set you up perfectly for skiing, and tasty afternoon tea treats will be ready to welcome you back ‘home’ each day. The attractive open plan dining room sets the scene for your evening meals including Le Savoie’s choice of menu.</p>
<h3>Why's this an Inghams Choice property?</h3>
<p><strong>Welcoming hotel team</strong> - The friendly hotel team are on hand to make your holiday enjoyable and restful. Throughout the week you can enjoy home cooked comforts and tasty afternoon tea, the staff will ensure all the tidying up is done for you - just sit back, relax and enjoy the fabulous skiing.</p>
<p><strong>Central location</strong> - The hotel benefits from having a central location in resort, so you are just a short walk away from the main ski lifts which take you up to the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes-Val d'Isere Ski Area</a></p>
<p><strong>Wellness area</strong> - With a fantastic wellness area and an indoor pool, this is a great choice for those looking for a spa hotel in Val d'Isere.</p>]]></description>
