  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Spa area with indoor pool, hot tub, sauna and steam room. Open from 4 - 7:30pm, with 13 years and over only after 5:30pm</li>
<li>Attractive restaurant</li>
<li>Residents only bar with adjacent lounge area</li>
<li>Separate lounge area with log fireplace</li>
<li>Ski room with heated boot warmers</li>
<li>Daily housekeeping (except Wednesdays)</li>
<li>Tea making facilities and Nespresso coffee machine in each room</li>
<li>L'Occitane toiletries</li>
<li>Free highspeed Wi-Fi throughout the hotel</li>
<li>Luggage storage</li>
<li>Breakfast in bed (available on request)</li>
<li>Laundry service (book and pay locally)</li>
</ul>
<p>We work with a local company Massage Me who manage the spa and offer a range of massages and beauty treatments (pay locally).</p>
<h2>Family Facilities</h2>
<p>The rooms and suites are ideal for family groups. many deluxe rooms interconnect and extra put-up beds can be added in many rooms for children.</p>
<ul>
<li>Cots are available for use in all bedrooms</li>
<li>Playroom, which is unsupervised </li>
<li>Highchairs in the restaurant</li>
</ul>
<h2>Family discount offers</h2>
<p>Book your next family ski holiday for winter 2024/25 and enjoy discounts when booking this family friendly hotel:</p>
<p><img style="width: 700px; height: 301px;" src="/media/13107261/1550-child-places-table-v2.jpg?width=700&amp;height=301&amp;mode=max" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/b02c4b0d30d346078ae06de65fc97c26" /></p>
