  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Central location in Val d'Isère</li>
<li>Shops and bars all within a few minutes' walk</li>
<li>Four minutes' walk (400 metres) to the three main high-speed lifts and ski school meeting place. </li>
<li>Bus stop just outside</li>
<li>Partner ski hire shop just outside the hotel</li>
</ul>
<p>The 10-person Solaise Gondola, complete with heated seats and Wi-Fi goes straight to the reshaped Solaise peak, in only seven minutes, from where a choice of lifts and runs fans out, including the connections across to the Le Fornet area and the superb snow of the Pissaillas Glacier.</p>
<p>There's also some additional beginner slopes, for all ages, right at the top of the Solaise gondola and a stylish Day Lodge with café, bar, games area and kids corner, complete with sun terraces and a picnic area so everyone can enjoy the spectacular views.</p>
<p>The Bellevarde Express chair or the Olympique gondola to access the Rocher de Bellevarde, with its long cruising runs down to La Daille, and the connections across the Tovière ridge to the wonders of Tignes.</p>]]></locationDescription>
