  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>En-suite bathroom with a bath and WC</li>
<li>Bathrobes and slippers</li>
<li>L'Occitane toiletries</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Mini fridge</li>
<li>Most rooms have a balcony with views of the resort</li>
</ul>
<h3>Ground Floor</h3>
<p>Entrance, stairs to reception, lifts to all floors. Spa area and ski storage</p>
<h3>First Floor</h3>
<p>Reception, restaurant, bar and lounge area.</p>
<h3>Second Floor</h3>
